We were also curious how longer passages in which the main protagonist in rising from the car and on foot. 
But as it is used for NFS, is in fact a lot differently than we had expected. 
Of course, there are potentially quite decent Arkade-Rennen, but, overall, the game will be diminished by some unnecessary mistakes in this series of more or less a few years are present. 
So it is not a mistake, but more signs of unbegreiflichen laziness in principle of game developers. 
The adventure begins very well. 
Firstly, it will be introduced into the story, whose main character, Jack certain issues of personal character; the only solution seems to be an illegal race across America. 
In San Francisco, on the west coast, to the steering wheel - with the task, as the first in New York. 
The basic idea involves a whole range of interesting elements. 
The entire route is in 10 stages and more than fifty individual race. 
This means that each race will be fought on the other route and that the various stages in various sufficiently diverse and interesting environment. 
There is no moment the impression that the game would continue to offer the same thing. 
Some areas are still very nice, even though the technical level of graphic display which goes beyond the earlier parts of the series. 
So no bewegende. 
But the journey through the desert, autumn landscape or high through deep snow landscape we have a very pleasant visual. 
