In the desert, for example, you will be surprised by a desert storm, which severely restricts the view. 
In the mountains, in turn, must be extremely careful that we will not be buried by an avalanche. 
By the way, are fairly well incorporated the individual race. 
Although only a few, but they are insufficient. 
For a while trying to overtake the prescribed number of opponents (in principle a classic race), then you have time to catch up (classic race against the stopwatch), then expect a personal duel with a single opponent. 
And also interfering with the police, who wants to blow the whole thing. 
A novelty are passages in which Jack leaves the car. 
This is more about some interactive Animations, in which Jack fleeing anybody else, and where he must help the players by pushing the right button at the right moment. 
So there is nothing complicated. 
It is surprising, however, that the game is much less of such passages, as one would expect (concrete only three). 
Ultimately, it is more likely to benefit, because this element has at least a chance to be boring - it is in the context of the above mentioned on the elements that make the game more. 
This model is in the Fußtapfes of the previous sections. 
In other words, from today's viewpoint, no trees, on the other hand, you could not claim that it would be a bad thing. 
Anyone who seeks realistic simulations must look elsewhere. 
But a troubled Rennfahren, the local model will continue to perform very well, even though the competition could be better. 
In the meantime, so far, everything is fine. 
Real problems are emerging only after a certain time. 
In contrast to the model, the model is not quite OK. 
From a game of this type, it is hard to expect that it is difficult to calculate Deformations and collisions, but if you virtually no impact on any idea how the car is, then it is obviously not everything is in order. 
A typical example: at the close or passing of oncoming cars "touched upon" the other car in some places only slightly in the other, almost identical situation but tailspin and wild performance. 
Or the same scrap metal. 
Thanks to the Restart-Systems is nothing more of it is annoying. 
The remaining arts are resolved: if you write-off or ends up far away from the route, then throws the game back to the last point of the route. 
Only - in every race, only five remaining arts. 
If you have exhausted them, everything is going on. 
Thus, the arts are more such a thing as a tool for the event that something does not succeed, but rely on it should not. 
Sometimes it helps, but not even the Restart, because nothing else helps to learn the critical section from the head. 
