As a lie revealed 
A glance at the current headlines shows how serious and widespread deception and lies in daily life. 
The Republican presidential candidate, Herman Cain, is dealing with the allegations of sexual harassment by several women, both sides accuse each other of lying. 
The leadership of Penh State is accused of the President's, since it has allegedly withheld reports, according to which a retired football coach boy was sexually abused. 
