The draw on Friday in Bosnia is forcing the Portuguese to reach a goal and win. 
A draw is the Bosnians, who is also a gateway, has already been enough. 
"This is a good result, but there is a certain amount of risk, because we have made no Auswärtstor," Bento regrets. 
"We will be able to compete against a team which has great technical qualities and possesses players with many individual qualities," he added. 
As has already been in Zenica, the Portuguese have already started to exert maximum pressure on the Bosnians, "they have no time for reflection." 
A good idea, under the condition that it will be implemented this time. 
